wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.ZS.def: External balance on goods and services (formerly resource balance) equals exports of goods and services minus imports of goods and services (previously nonfactor services).
wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.ZS.name: External balance on goods and services
wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.ZS.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
